    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, characterized by its eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example utilizes a 6-speed manual gearbox paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the weight-saving factory carbon fiber roof. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of this naturally aspirated icon. Minimal cosmetic wear consistent with enthusiast use.",
